latest_work_xp.description:
As a Lay Mission Partner(LMP), we need to know and learn how the media center runs. Every month, we shift tasks/roles. These are the following roles:

1. Cashier(Girls only) - We receive payments from our dear customers. Before closing, we do the Resoconto, for us to know how much is the profit for the day and how much money is left in the drawer that will serves as a "change" for the following day transactions.

2. Customer Assistant - Assisting the customers while they look for their desired books or items.

Assisting them to where they will find an item or sometimes giving them advise on what to buy.

3. Inventory Clerk - Listing items that must be displayed and refilled. When doing the inventory, we also take note items that are lacking and having extras.

4. Receiving Clerk - Receiving deliveries and checking if all the items are in good condition and complete.

5. Item Analyst - Encoding and marking up items to come up with a good price.
